item.title: CVE-2020-14544|2024-09-27T18:42:40.599Z -- oracle%20corporation -- transportation%20management
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle Transportation Management product of Oracle Supply Chain (component: Data, Domain & Function Security). The supported version that is affected is 6.4.3. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows low privileged attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle Transportation Management. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized read access to a subset of Oracle Transportation Management accessible data. CVSS 3.1 Base Score 4.3 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N).
